Package: coreact
Title: High-Performance Co-reactivity Analysis
Version: 1.2.0
Authors@R: person("August F.", "Jernbom", , "ajernbom@jhmi.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7773-1851"))
Description: Optimized pipeline for calculating co-occurrence statistics (Hypergeometric test, Jaccard index, Overlap coefficient) 
    between two sparse matrices. Uses adaptive matrix/vector algebra and parallel processing.
